<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ngai tie, van Lal Cha chu Bethlehem bawng In tawmah
 Hingmi vawnchawih in A hung pieng a;
 A lal lopina, van chutphah chu hun nusie'n,
 Ei tan dingin bawng In tawmah A hung pieng hi.

[V2]
 Ka hun lawp ui lei leh van Lal lopi,
 Theihtawp in na pakna la sa'ng kau;
 Liengvaite leh gimtheite Lalpa,
 Ma khan Bethlehem ah nang di'n mun a um puoi;
 Tuhin vang Nang di'n mun a um ka lak u-ah.

[V3]
 2. A pienna mun tawm tak Bethlehem bawng In lo chu,
 Amah dingin mundang a um puoi;
 A lu A nga tai, Bethlehem bawng In tawm ah,
 Lei lalte leh Amah miten a na deih puou.

[V4]
 3. Lal chungnung mun chungnung pena chengsa Lal Isu,
 Lei lalte'n Amah do mahleule,
 Kei a dingin vang Lal deihum pen a hi ie,
 Liengvai I kipahna dinga Lal hung pieng hi.

[V5]
 4. Ma khan Eden huona hinna Kraun lul I mansak,
 Tuhin Lalpa'n ei muh sak kit tai,
 Apau kamsuok hehpihna, liengvai ei nempen,
 Zingsawl Aksi sanga vak hawih Lal deihum hi.

[V6]
 5. Ma khan chu Bethlehem ah Nang di'n mun a um puoi,
 Nang mithiengtho van Lal penna di'n;
 Tuhin vang ziehin Nanga di'n mun a um hi,
 Isu ka kawm u-ah chengin, ei umpih in.</lyrics>
<title>Bethlehem ah mun a um puoi</title>
<hymn_number>23</hymn_number>
</song>